          <div>
            <div class="work-metric-value">32<em>&uarr;</em></div>
            <div class="work-metric-label">Mockups shipped</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="work-metric-value">20<em>+</em></div>
            <div class="work-metric-label">Pages designed</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="work-visual" style="overflow:hidden; min-height:320px;">
        <div class="work-corner"><ph-arrow-up-right weight="regular" size="20"></ph-arrow-up-right></div>
        <img src="/images/aed/aed-main-thumnail.png" alt="AED Dashboard" style="width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; transition: transform 0.6s var(--ease);" onmouseover="this.style.transform='scale(1.05)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='scale(1)'" />
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- Case 2 -->
    <a href="#" class="work-card reveal" data-cursor="View case">
      <div class="work-card-meta">
        <div class="work-num">&#8470; 02 / JujuTok</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="work-title">6 AI agents,<br/>4 debates,<br/>one verdict.</h3>
          <p class="work-sub">Multi-agent stock analysis platform. Designed the bias-mitigation structure where 4 investor personas debate before concluding. Planned and shipped alone.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="work-details">
          <div class="work-info">
            <div class="work-info-item">
              <span class="work-info-label">Type</span>
              <span class="work-info-value">Solo Build</span>
            </div>
            <div class="work-info-item">
              <span class="work-info-label">Role</span>
              <span class="work-info-value">PM + Engineer</span>
            </div>
            <div class="work-info-item">
              <span class="work-info-label">Year</span>
              <span class="work-info-value">2025</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="work-metrics">
            <div>
              <div class="work-metric-value">6</div>
              <div class="work-metric-label">Agent types</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="work-metric-value">31<em>k</em></div>
              <div class="work-metric-label">LOC solo</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="work-visual">
        <div class="blob blob-1" style="background: #6884A0;"></div>
        <div class="blob blob-2" style="background: #3D8268;"></div>
        <div class="work-corner"><ph-arrow-up-right weight="regular" size="20"></ph-arrow-up-right></div>
        <div class="work-mock">
          <div class="mock-bar md"></div>
          <div class="mock-bar lg"></div>
          <div class="mock-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);">
            <div class="mock-cell"></div>
            <div class="mock-cell accent"></div>
            <div class="mock-cell"></div>
            <div class="mock-cell"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mock-bar sm"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- Case 3 -->
    <a href="#" class="work-card reveal" data-cursor="View case">
      <div class="work-card-meta">
        <div class="work-num">&#8470; 03 / RATB <span class="wip-badge">WIP</span></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="work-title">Passed<br/>national<br/>review — 3&times;.</h3>
          <p class="work-sub">Robo-advisor algorithm operations. Scaled planning from 2 &rarr; 8 &rarr; 28 strategies across three rounds. All passed regulatory review.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="work-details">
          <div class="work-info">
            <div class="work-info-item">
              <span class="work-info-label">Company</span>
              <span class="work-info-value">AssetPlus</span>
            </div>
            <div class="work-info-item">
              <span class="work-info-label">Role</span>
              <span class="work-info-value">Algorithm Planner</span>
            </div>
            <div class="work-info-item">
              <span class="work-info-label">Year</span>
              <span class="work-info-value">2022 — 2024</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="work-metrics">
            <div>
              <div class="work-metric-value">38</div>
              <div class="work-metric-label">Algorithms</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="work-metric-value">3<em>/3</em></div>
              <div class="work-metric-label">Rounds passed</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="work-visual">
        <div class="blob blob-1" style="background: #D4833D;"></div>
        <div class="blob blob-2" style="background: #7E6EA0;"></div>
        <div class="work-corner"><ph-arrow-up-right weight="regular" size="20"></ph-arrow-up-right></div>
        <div class="work-mock">
          <div class="mock-bar lg"></div>
          <div class="mock-bar md"></div>
          <div style="height: 60px; background: linear-gradient(to top right, var(--border), transparent); border-radius: 4px; margin: 8px 0; position: relative;">
            <div style="position: absolute; right: 20%; top: 30%; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent);"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mock-bar sm"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- About -->
<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="section-head reveal">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">02 / About</p>
      <h2 class="section-title syne">A planner<br/>who <em>ships</em>.</h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-grid reveal">
    <div>
      <p class="about-lead">
        Finance-trained, systems-minded. I find the missing taxonomy behind "add search," and build the spec that ships.
      </p>
      <p class="about-body">
        At AssetPlus Asset Management, I planned 38 AI investment algorithms and passed national regulatory review, while managing 200+ live accounts. Now at Alphabridge, I'm redesigning the strategy analysis dashboard used daily by the quant research team. On a team with no designer, I designed 20+ analysis pages and solo-built a multi-agent stock analysis platform from spec to deployment.
      </p>
      <a href="/ko/resume" class="view-cv" data-cursor="Resume">
        Resume <ph-arrow-up-right weight="regular" size="14"></ph-arrow-up-right>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="about-details">
        <div>
          <p class="about-kv-label">Education</p>
          <p class="about-kv-value">Johns Hopkins University<br/>B.A. Economics · Minor in Marketing</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="about-kv-label">Current</p>
          <p class="about-kv-value">Alphabridge<br/>2025 — Now</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="about-kv-label">Domain</p>
          <p class="about-kv-value">Finance &middot; AI<br/>Robo-advisor</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="about-kv-label">Stack</p>
          <p class="about-kv-value">Figma &middot; Next.js<br/>FastAPI &middot; Claude</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skills">
        <span class="skill-pill">Service Planning</span>
        <span class="skill-pill">AI Agents</span>
        <span class="skill-pill">Finance</span>
        <span class="skill-pill">IA Design</span>
        <span class="skill-pill">Prototyping</span>
        <span class="skill-pill">UX Research</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact -->
<section class="contact" id="contact">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="section-label">03 / Get in touch</p>
    <h2 class="contact-title syne">Plan.<br/>Build.<br/><em>Prove.</em></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="contact-grid reveal">
    <div class="contact-item">
      <span class="section-label">Email</span>
      <a href="mailto:elliebinn@gmail.com" data-cursor="Copy">elliebinn@gmail.com <ph-copy weight="regular" size="14"></ph-copy></a>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-item">
      <span class="section-label">LinkedIn</span>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/hyebin-woo" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-cursor="Visit">hyebin-woo <ph-arrow-up-right weight="regular" size="14"></ph-arrow-up-right></a>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-item">
      <span class="section-label">GitHub</span>
      <a href="https://github.com/Elliebinn" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-cursor="Visit">Elliebinn <ph-arrow-up-right weight="regular" size="14"></ph-arrow-up-right></a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2026 Hyebin Woo &middot; Made in Seoul</p>
    <p>Portfolio mockup v1</p>
  </footer>
</section>

<script>
  // Preloader — show only once per session
  const preloader = document.getElementById('preloader');
  if (sessionStorage.getItem('preloaded')) {
    preloader.classList.add('done');
  } else {
    window.addEventListener('load', () => {
      setTimeout(() => {
        preloader.classList.add('done');
        sessionStorage.setItem('preloaded', '1');
      }, 1400);
    });
  }

  // Nav scroll — brand slides from left, links from right, merge into pill
  const nav = document.getElementById('nav');
  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    if (window.scrollY > 60) nav.classList.add('scrolled');
    else nav.classList.remove('scrolled');
    lastY = y;
  });

  // Scroll indicator
  const scrollFill = document.getElementById('scrollFill');
  const scrollIndicator = document.getElementById('scrollIndicator');
  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    const pct = Math.min(100, (window.scrollY / (document.body.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight)) * 100);
    scrollFill.style.height = pct + '%';
    if (pct > 95) scrollIndicator.classList.add('hidden');
    else scrollIndicator.classList.remove('hidden');
  });

  // Custom cursor — ring + dot
  const cursor = document.getElementById('cursor');
  const cursorLabel = document.getElementById('cursorLabel');
  let mx = 0, my = 0, cx = 0, cy = 0;
  document.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => { mx = e.clientX; my = e.clientY; });
  function loop() {
    cx += (mx - cx) * 0.5; cy += (my - cy) * 0.5;
    cursor.style.transform = `translate(${cx}px, ${cy}px)`;
    requestAnimationFrame(loop);
  }
  loop();

  document.querySelectorAll('[data-cursor]').forEach(el => {
    el.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
      cursor.classList.add('hover', 'has-label');
      cursorLabel.textContent = el.dataset.cursor;
    });
    el.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
      cursor.classList.remove('hover', 'has-label');
    });
  });
  document.querySelectorAll('a, button').forEach(el => {
    if (!el.dataset.cursor) {
      el.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => cursor.classList.add('hover'));
      el.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => cursor.classList.remove('hover'));
    }
  });

  // Copy email
  document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="mailto:"]').forEach(a => {
    a.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      const email = a.href.replace('mailto:', '');
      navigator.clipboard?.writeText(email);
      cursorLabel.textContent = 'Copied ✓';
      setTimeout(() => { cursorLabel.textContent = 'Copy'; }, 1500);
    });
  });

  // Theme toggle
  const toggle = document.getElementById('themeToggle');
  const themeIcon = document.getElementById('themeIcon');
  const saved = localStorage.getItem('hb-theme');
  if (saved) document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', saved);
  function updateIcon() {
    const t = document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-theme');
    themeIcon.outerHTML = t === 'dark'
      ? '<ph-sun weight="regular" size="16" id="themeIcon"></ph-sun>'
      : '<ph-moon weight="regular" size="16" id="themeIcon"></ph-moon>';
  }
  updateIcon();
  toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const cur = document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-theme');
    const next = cur === 'dark' ? 'light' : 'dark';
    document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', next);
    localStorage.setItem('hb-theme', next);
    updateIcon();
  });

  // Reveal
  const io = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(e => {
      if (e.isIntersecting) { e.target.classList.add('visible'); io.unobserve(e.target); }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.15 });
  document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => io.observe(el));
</script>

</V2Layout>
